msgid ""
"MetadataSync (MDSync) is the metadata & data synchronization solution for "
"DHIS2. It allows easy metadata mapping, distribution and the automatization "
"of synchronization of data and metadata. MDSync is also a versatile "
"solution for DHIS2 metadata packages generation, validation and "
"distribution, providing graphical interfaces for such time-consuming "
"operations."
msgstr ""
"MetadataSync (MDSync) is the metadata & data synchronization solution for "
"DHIS2. It allows easy metadata mapping, distribution and the automatization "
"of synchronization of data and metadata. MDSync is also a versatile "
"solution for DHIS2 metadata packages generation, validation and "
"distribution, providing graphical interfaces for such time-consuming "
"operations."

